    "title": "Drug Localization Variants — INN/US/UK + CIS Brand Names",
    "purpose": "Free-text drug name resolution with localization support across International (INN), US (USAN), UK (BAN), and CIS (Russian/Uzbek/CIS-brand) name variants. Powers L2-1 Ontology Normalizer and L2-15 Multi-Language Drug Resolver.",
    "scope": "DEMO and RESEARCH environments only. clinician_prod must use the live composite source: (a) RxNorm REST for INN/US/UK/brand resolution, (b) UZ Ministry of Health drug registry for Uzbek/Russian variants. RxNorm is wired in Session B; UZ MOH connector is Session F target.",
    "snapshot_origin": "Manually curated from RxNorm + UZ State Drug Register + Russian Federation State Register of Medicines (ГРЛС).",
